    <section class="section bg-cream" id="activities">

        <div class="section-head fade">

            <span class="eyebrow">The Catalogue</span>

            <h2 class="section-title">Experiences for <em>every kind</em> of team</h2>

            <p class="section-sub">Every session happens at your office premises. Pick a category, pick an

                experience — Sowaka handles everything else.</p>

        </div>

        <div class="act-tabs">

            <button class="act-tab active" data-panel="active">Active &amp; Physical</button>

            <button class="act-tab" data-panel="mind">Mind &amp; Wellbeing</button>

            <button class="act-tab" data-panel="creative">Creative &amp; Therapeutic</button>

            <button class="act-tab" data-panel="knowledge">Health &amp; Knowledge</button>

            <button class="act-tab" data-panel="ld">Learning &amp; Development</button>

        </div>

        <div class="act-panels">



            <div class="act-panel active" id="panel-active">

                <div class="act-card act-hero">

                    <div class="act-icon-wrap">🏆</div>

                    <div class="act-body">

                        <h3>Circuit Challenge</h3>

                        <p>A week-long fitness programme where teams compete across daily workouts, fitness tasks,

                            and stretching streaks, culminating in a relay-style obstacle race inspired by Hyrox and

                            Devil Circuit. Guaranteed high point for every employee — fit or not.</p>

                    </div>

                    <span class="act-pill">Most Popular</span>

                </div>

                <div class="act-card">

                    <div class="act-icon-wrap">🎉</div>

                    <div class="act-body">

                        <h3>Office Olympics</h3>

                        <p>The floor is split into teams competing across physical challenges. A great way to get

                            everyone moving — and an even better opportunity for genuine team bonding.</p>

                    </div>

                </div>

                <div class="act-card">

                    <div class="act-icon-wrap">💃</div>

                    <div class="act-body">

                        <h3>Grooves — Zumba &amp; Dance</h3>

                        <p>Sometimes Masala Bhangra, sometimes Bollywood fusion, sometimes team dance-offs between

                            bays. Always creative, always inclusive. Maximum fun on the office floor.</p>

                    </div>

                </div>

                <div class="act-card">

                    <div class="act-icon-wrap">🥊</div>

                    <div class="act-body">

                        <h3>Self Defense &amp; Kickboxing</h3>

                        <p>Self defense is about escape mindset, not fighting. The kickboxing coach brings all

                            equipment — real kicks, real punches, real stress relief. Especially great for women.

                        </p>

                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>



            <div class="act-panel" id="panel-mind">

                <div class="act-card act-hero">

                    <div class="act-icon-wrap">🧘</div>

                    <div class="act-body">

                        <h3>Yoga &amp; Meditation</h3>

                        <p>Sessions include guided meditation, face yoga, and breathwork — highly customised based

                            on job roles, gamified on request. Addresses sleep issues, anxiety, energy crashes,

                            spine pain, eye strain, and wrist strain. Proven and powerful.</p>

                    </div>

                    <span class="act-pill">Team Favourite</span>

                </div>

                <div class="act-card">

                    <div class="act-icon-wrap">🎶</div>

                    <div class="act-body">

                        <h3>Sound Therapy</h3>

                        <p>Singing bowls and chimes guide the brain into a state of no thoughts. Extremely relaxing

                            after high-pressure periods. The perfect introduction to meditation for beginners.</p>

                    </div>

                </div>

                <div class="act-card">

                    <div class="act-icon-wrap">💚</div>

                    <div class="act-body">

                        <h3>Emotional Wellbeing</h3>

                        <p>Not a generic stress lecture. Customised to your team's specific context and stressors —

                            employees learn to recognise negative emotions and build practical coping techniques.

                        </p>

                    </div>

                </div>

                <div class="act-card">

                    <div class="act-icon-wrap">🪑</div>

                    <div class="act-body">

                        <h3>Ergonomics</h3>

                        <p>A physio-led session blending tips, games, and stretches. Essential relief for the

                            cumulative physical toll of 8+ hours of sitting at a desk every single day.</p>

                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>



            <div class="act-panel" id="panel-creative">

                <div class="act-card act-hero">

                    <div class="act-icon-wrap">🎨</div>

                    <div class="act-body">

                        <h3>Creative Expression — Art Workshop</h3>

                        <p>Teams paint bags, mugs, and coasters they take home or display at their desks. Time off

                            screens, creative brain engagement, and the dopamine of completing something beautiful —

                            all proven to meaningfully reduce stress levels.</p>

                    </div>

                    <span class="act-pill">Most Requested</span>

                </div>

                <div class="act-card">

                    <div class="act-icon-wrap">🏺</div>

                    <div class="act-body">

                        <h3>Pottery Workshop</h3>

                        <p>Guided wheel pottery — the experience of building something from clay with your own hands

                            is deeply rewarding and unlike any other office activity your team has tried.</p>

                    </div>

                </div>

                <div class="act-card">

                    <div class="act-icon-wrap">🌱</div>

                    <div class="act-body">

                        <h3>Gardening &amp; Soil Therapy</h3>

                        <p>Hands in the earth, close to nature. One of the most calming and grounding experiences

                            available — and employees leave with something alive to care for at their desks.</p>

                    </div>

                </div>

                <div class="act-card">

                    <div class="act-icon-wrap">🤲</div>

                    <div class="act-body">

                        <h3>Clay Sculpting</h3>

                        <p>A tactile, meditative group session where teams create clay sculptures. No experience

                            needed — just willingness to get hands messy and minds quiet.</p>

                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>



            <div class="act-panel" id="panel-knowledge">

                <div class="act-card act-hero">

                    <div class="act-icon-wrap">💰</div>

                    <div class="act-body">

                        <h3>Financial Planning Workshop</h3>

                        <p>Actionable, not just gyaan. Delivered with a hands-on Excel tool, breaking financial

                            planning into four clear steps: insurance, tracking inflow and outflow, setting

                            objectives, and investing. Directly addresses the universal stressor — money.</p>

                    </div>

                    <span class="act-pill">High Impact</span>

                </div>

                <div class="act-card">

                    <div class="act-icon-wrap">🔬</div>

                    <div class="act-body">

                        <h3>Myth Buster Polling</h3>

                        <p>Health topics — nutrition, skincare, PCOS, diabetes, hypothyroidism — turned into live

                            interactive polling. Cuts through marketing gimmicks and empowers real decisions.</p>

                    </div>

                </div>

                <div class="act-card">

                    <div class="act-icon-wrap">🩺</div>

                    <div class="act-body">

                        <h3>Body Scans &amp; Check-ups</h3>

                        <p>BCA scans, BP check-ups, and annual health check-ups done at your office. Nothing

                            triggers action and healthy behaviour change like a red flag on your own reports.</p>

                    </div>

                </div>

                <div class="act-card">

                    <div class="act-icon-wrap">📈</div>

                    <div class="act-body">

                        <h3>Workplace Effectiveness</h3>

                        <p>Communication, collaboration, influence, and leadership — through experiential learning

                            only. No lectures. Includes procrastination and motivation assessments to boost

                            productivity.</p>

                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>



            <div class="act-panel" id="panel-ld">

                <div class="act-card act-hero">

                    <div class="act-icon-wrap">🏆</div>

                    <div class="act-body">

                        <h3>CXO Leadership Session</h3>

                        <p>We build leaders who can translate intent into execution — aligning teams, owning

                            outcomes, and reducing dependency on the founder.</p>

                    </div>

                    <span class="act-pill">Star Product</span>

                </div>

                <div class="act-card">

                    <div class="act-icon-wrap">📊</div>

                    <div class="act-body">

                        <h3>Mid Manager Training</h3>

                        <p>We equip managers to translate strategy into execution — aligning teams, unblocking work,

                            and ensuring things actually move forward.</p>

                    </div>

                </div>

                <div class="act-card">

                    <div class="act-icon-wrap">🌱</div>

                    <div class="act-body">

                        <h3>First Time Managers Program</h3>

                        <p>We help individual contributors step into management with clarity — shifting from doing

                            the work to enabling others to deliver.</p>

                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>



        </div>

    </section>



